 ('15', '15', 'en_us', 'The game', '<p>The ten concerts, nine of which I\'ve attended game:</p><ol><li>The Monkees</li><li>Camper Van Beethoven</li><li>The Dead Milkmen</li><li>REM</li><li>Depeche Mode</li><li>The Eagles</li><li>Jane\'s Addiction</li><li>Pharoah Sanders</li><li>Johnny Cash</li><li>Southern Culture on the Skids</li></ol>', NULL, '2017-04-30 22:52:56', '2017-04-30 22:52:56', 'e3d9dd67-a22f-4934-99e5-82459aa8c869'),
 ('16', '16', 'en_us', 'Wishes', '<p>I really wish I could find my Tiny Lights CDs.  I want to say that Ween\'s <cite>Roses Are Free</cite> is a straight up theft of a song on <cite>Milky Juicy</cite>.  Which is understandable since TL\'s bassist went on to play bass for Ween.</p>', NULL, '2017-04-30 22:54:54', '2017-04-30 22:55:52', '9736a5df-2261-415d-95fc-b697dc8a0245'),
